entries.content: Log cleanup task: Remove verbose chunk logging while preserving event logs. Found extensive per-chunk logging in streaming pipeline (ChunkLogger, StreamingChunkRouter, AgentMessagesManager, ToolChunkTransformer). Must preserve: ThreadId extraction, auto-completion events, tool execution events, stream lifecycle logs.

Log cleanup completed: Removed 11 verbose chunk logging statements across 4 files (StreamingChunkRouter: 5, AgentMessagesManager: 4, ChunkProcessor: 1, ToolChunkTransformer: 2). Preserved all important event logs (ThreadId extraction, tool events, auto-completion, lifecycle). Console output now clean while maintaining critical debugging information.
